But I want to let everyone know, we aren't content just to ride the wave of demand getting better. And as we've said over the years, we want to continue to create our own recovery, which is – and we talked a little bit about it today is focused on cost reductions and we're doing that through Lean Six Sigma and advanced manufacturing. With product innovation, we're going to continue to deliver product extensions. I said we introduced 15 new products to 20 new products, but we also have some big ideas that we have in the pipeline that we hope to share with you soon, but most importantly, having our customers top of mind every single day.
We're very focused on customer satisfaction and really delighting our customers. So we're going to continue to strengthen, diversify and differentiate. And we really appreciate your interest in USG today, and we'll talk to you next quarter. Thank you very much.
