James S. Metcalf 
Executive Compensation
As Former Chairman, President and Chief Executive Officer at USG CORP, James S. Metcalf  made $7,107,288 in total compensation.  Of this total $870,000 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $6,181,197 was awarded as stock and $56,091 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


