The chart on this page features a breakdown of the total annual pay for James S. Metcalf ,  Former Chairman, President and Chief Executive Officer at USG CORP as reported in their proxy statements. 
Total Cash Compensation information is comprised of yearly Base Pay and Bonuses. USG CORP income statements for executive base pay and bonus are filed yearly with the SEC in the edgar filing system. USG CORP annual reports of executive compensation and pay are most commonly found in the Def 14a documents.
Total Equity aggregates grant date fair value of stock and option awards and long term incentives granted during the fiscal year.
Other Compensation covers all compensation-like awards that don't fit in any of these other standard categories. Numbers reported do not include change in pension value and non-qualified deferred compensation earnings.



